{
  "stem": "27770.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Because if I go down, they wouldn't say that I go down to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They would tell me you came to steal from the children, bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So the same plate which I ate the soup daytime, I had to urinate into the plate, keep it there by the bed, and in morning throw it out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Because it's still better than to get killed because I'm going to steal bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "After a month and a half, yeah, there was a very interesting place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Everybody was asking me outside I should-- if I'm in kitchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They knew I'm in kitchen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And the Polish guys, they trusted me, who went to the commander.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Especially this Moshe, who knew already I can get potatoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He says, bring-- bring more potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I said, Moshe, it's not so easy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "If they catch me, we have there a couple, a Greek guy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And this Greek guy always used to say [GREEK].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "[GREEK] means, probably, no stealing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "One guy, what-- a guy, they caught him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they gave him 25 from behind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But still, and when they me more even than besides potatoes, they told me, bring us salt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You get for salt, everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You get cigarette.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You get bread.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, why the hell you need so much salt?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, when we have a portion of bread, and we put a lot of salt, we're drinking a lot of water after it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if the stomach is full, who cares with what, what as long as it's full, we are full.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are not hungry!",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I figure myself, I have to do something about it to get to the-- to the salt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I made fast my job, in order to go faster.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
